items.headline: Welcome to the Daily Lives of High School Boys Wikia!
items.desc: This Wikia is dedicated to the Daily Lives of High School Boys Anime and Manga. Right now, Daily Lives of High School Boys Wiki needs a lot of your help. Anyone can help out just by adding info and sharing anything you know about the Danshi Koukousei no Nichijou anime or the Danshi Koukousei no Nichijou manga, though the best way to start adding info is by editing articles that need more info. You can also help by adding a photo. We'll be counting on you! Thank you so much for your time!
